data.description:
This beautiful ranch-style home is now available for immediate move-in! It features three bedrooms and one and a half bathrooms. The eat-in kitchen has been recently updated with sleek stainless steel appliances, a spacious pantry with convenient pull-out drawers, and a stylish stainless steel farm sink. All the kitchen drawers are soft-close. The living room and all three bedrooms showcase beautiful hardwood flooring, while the kitchen boasts luxury vinyl flooring. The property is situated on a .52-acre lot, providing ample space for children, pets, and outdoor entertainment. You can get very creative with it!

The following updates have been made: Septic System in 2021, Most of the plumbing in 2021, Underground electric dog fence in 2022, Driveway apron, and drain pipe replaced in 2023, Roof 2020.
